A support customer would like the means of modifying the possible values (options) of an existing custom field. 

The custom field stores mobile phone headset models. There are up to 300 of them and they change frequently. 

You can specify options when you create a new custom field: CreateCustomField tag with AddCustomFieldSelectValue sub-tag. However there is no means to modify the values of an existing custom field.

