We would like the ability to programmatically modify (via SOAP) user attributes such as fullname and SMTP mail addresses.  We could perform such modifications by hand, via the web interface for small changes or via the export/modify/import mechanism for larger changes such as changing all of the e-mail address domains, but this doesn't improve our automated process.  We currently run a custom program that daily synchronizes user information between our LDAP server and JIRA, via JIRA's SOAP-based service.  Without the ability to programmatically modify user attributes, we are forced to do by hand what could more safely and efficiently be done programmatically.
